import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { BrowserRouter as Router } from 'react-router-dom'
import App from './App'
import Theme from './context/Theme'

ReactDOM.render( <
    Router >
    <
    Theme >
    <
    App / > < /Theme> <
    /Router>, document.getElementById('root'))
